2023 (Establishment Day) Order 2023.

title: for the purposes of the Agricultural and Food Supply Chain Act 2023 (No. 19
heading: 2. The 13th day of December 2023 is appointed as the establishment day
text_raw:
2. The 13th day of December 2023 is appointed as the establishment day 
for the purposes of the Agricultural and Food Supply Chain Act 2023 (No. 19 
of 2023). 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

12 December, 2023. 

CHARLIE MCCONALOGUE, 

Minister for Agriculture, Food and the Marine. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 15th December, 2023.
